'''Ryloth Ventures''' was a trade-based corporation located on [[Ryloth/Legends|Ryloth]]. During the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]], it was headed by [[Has Doneeta]], with [[Tholme/Legends|Miles Croft]] as a business negotiator. [[Senator/Legends|Senator]] [[Vien'sai'Malloc]] was interested in having Ryloth Ventures trade on [[Devaron/Legends|Devaron]].

Presumably Ryloth Ventures was a real corporation; however, as it was part of a backstory given by the undercover [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]] [[Aayla Secura/Legends|Aayla Secura]], [[The Dark Woman|An'ya Kuro]], and [[Tholme/Legends|Tholme]], the amount of truth to it is not known.

